er sees their matches\n   173\t    Given Alice has matched with Bob and Charlie\
n   174\t    When Alice opens the match list\n   175\t    Then she should see Bo
b and Charlie ordered by match creation time descending\n   176\t    And each it
em should show the matched user\'s nickname, avatar, and match time\n   177\t```
\n   178\t\n   179\t#### 技术要求\n   180\t- 接口：`GET /matches?limit=20&cursor
=`（游标分页）。\n   181\t- 查询当前用户参与的 `matches` 中 `status = \'matched\
