        is_error=False,
        output='# Dev Tools 模块实现\n\n## 职责\n\nDebug 专用工具模块，仅在开发
模式下可见。提供悬浮抽屉入口，支持运行时修改 Server Base URL 并持久化到本地存储
，用于开发/测试环境快速切换后端地址。\n\n## 关联文档\n\n- **PRD**: [prd/v1-dev-t
ools-drawer.md](../../prd/v1-dev-tools-drawer.md)\n- **BDD**: [tests/bdd/dev_too
ls_drawer.feature](../../tests/bdd/dev_tools_drawer.feature)\n- **设计规范**: [d
esign-spec.md](../../designs/issue-29/design-spec.md)\n- **高保真原型**: [mockup
.html](../../designs/issue-29/mockup.html)\n- **低保真线框图**: [wireframe.svg](
../../designs/issue-29/wireframe.svg)\n\n## 流程图\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagra
m\n    participant U as 开发者\n    participant T as DevToolsToggleButton\n    p
articipant D as DevToolsDrawer\n    participant S as ServerUrlTool\n    particip
ant C as DevToolsCubit\n    participant R as DevToolsRepository\n    participant
P as SharedPreferences\n    participant Dio as DioClient\n\n    U->>T: 点击悬浮
按钮\n    T->>D: 触发 onToggle\n    D->>S: 展开抽屉，显示 URL 编辑卡片\n    U->>
S: 输入新的 Server Base URL\n    S->>C: onUrlChanged(url)\n    C->>C: 校验 URL 
格式\n    alt URL 格式非法\n        C-->>S: urlError = "请输入有效的 HTTP/HTTPS 
URL"\n        S->>S: 输入框边框变红，保存按钮置灰\n    else URL 格式合法\n      
 C-->>S: urlError = ""\n        S->>S: 保存按钮可用\n        U->>S: 点击保存\n  
     S->>C: save()\n        C->>R: saveServerBaseUrl(url)\n        R->>P: setStr
ing(\'dev_tools_server_base_url\', url)\n        P-->>R: 写入成功\n        R-->>
C: 完成\n        C-->>S: saveSuccess = true\n        S->>Dio: 更新 baseUrl\n    
   S->>S: 显示 SnackBar "保存成功，新配置已生效"\n    end\n```\n\n## 关键文件\n\
n| 文件 | 路径 |\n|------|------|\n| DevToolsWrapper | `apps/mobile/lib/presenta
tion/widgets/dev_tools_wrapper.dart` |\n| DevToolsToggleButton | `apps/mobile/li
b/presentation/widgets/dev_tools_toggle_button.dart` |\n| DevToolsDrawer | `apps
/mobile/lib/presentation/widgets/dev_tools_drawer.dart` |\n| ServerUrlTool | `ap
ps/mobile/lib/presentation/widgets/server_url_tool.dart` |\n| Cubit | `apps/mobi
le/lib/presentation/blocs/dev_tools/dev_tools_cubit.dart` |\n| State | `apps/mob
ile/lib/presentation/blocs/dev_tools/dev_tools_state.dart` |\n| Repository 接口 
| `apps/mobile/lib/domain/repositories/dev_tools_repository.dart` |\n| Repositor
y 实现 | `apps/mobile/lib/data/repositories/dev_tools_repository_impl.dart` |\n\
n## 条件编译说明\n\n为避免调试代码进入 Release 产物，必须在 `MaterialApp.router`
的 `builder` 中通过 `kDebugMode` 条件注入 `DevToolsWrapper`：\n\n```dart\n// app
s/mobile/lib/app.dart\nWidget build(BuildContext context) {\n  return MaterialAp
p.router(\n    // ...\n    builder: (context, child) {\n      if (kDebugMode) {\
n        return DevToolsWrapper(child: child!);\n      }\n      return child!;\n
   },\n  );\n}\n```\n\n- `DevToolsWrapper` 负责在 Debug 模式下挂载 `DevToolsTogg
leButton` 与 `DevToolsDrawer`。\n- Release 模式下该分支被编译器排除，`DevToolsWr
apper` 不会被打包进产物。\n- 与调试相关的 Repository、Cubit 注册同样建议在 `kDeb
ugMode` 分支下完成，以减小组包体积。\n\n## 边界情况\n\n1. **Release 模式排除**：
所有调试 Widget 必须包裹在 `if (kDebugMode) ...` 中，Release 模式下不编译进产物
。\n2. **URL 校验失败**：空值或格式错误时，输入框显示红色错误边框与文案，保存按
钮禁用。\n3. **SharedPreferences 异常**：读写失败时静默捕获，避免阻塞主流程；保
存失败时显示错误提示。\n4. **抽屉关闭后状态保留**：再次打开抽屉时保留上次输入内
容（未保存），避免误操作丢失编辑内容。\n\n## 全链路变更清单\n\n修改本模块时，Age
nt 需要同时检查并更新以下文件：\n\n1. **移动端 Widget**：`apps/mobile/lib/presen
tation/widgets/dev_tools_*.dart`\n2. **移动端状态管理**：`apps/mobile/lib/presen
tation/blocs/dev_tools/`\n3. **移动端 Repository**：`apps/mobile/lib/data/reposi
tories/dev_tools_repository_impl.dart`\n4. **BDD 测试**：`tests/bdd/dev_tools_dr
awer.feature`\n5. **模块文档**：`docs/modules/dev-tools.md`\n6. **Flutter 规范文
档**：`docs/design-docs/flutter.md`\n',
